{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>You awaken amidst a sea of scrap, without memories. Fight to survive. Explore a treacherous wasteland. Discover who you are now.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Exsys is an action-packed adventure that blends classic 90s beat-'em-up gameplay with modern Action RPG elements. Explore a stunning 3D world of scrap and danger.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Feature</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Free Combo system:</strong> <br>Break free from rigid combos! Unleash devastating combos with free-flowing combat. Chain attacks and commands to create your own unique fighting style.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1116350/extras/seq_GIF_Fight_01.gif?t=1736216163\" /></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Active Skill System:</strong> <br>Discover skills in the form of equipable items. Mix and match to tailor your combat style. Use fighting game-style commands to unleash their power.  <br>Mix, match, and order a skill with the same command to create a chain of moves that execute in order.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1116350/extras/seq_GIF_Fight_03.gif?t=1736216163\" /></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Item system: </strong>Collect and utilize a variety of items to buff your stats, debuff enemies, and unleash special attacks. Equip up to 4 items in your quick slots for easy access during combat. Combine items and skills to create a unique fighting style and survive the harsh world of scrap.   <br><strong>Store items in the stash for your next character.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1116350/extras/seq_GIF_Itemuse_01.gif?t=1736216163\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>\tYour character lives only once. If your character dies, you lose everything on that character and start the new game with a new character.  <br>   </strong></p></li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Awakening","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1116350/f53885933e243df9ff846489fcdcc904e42643d7.jpg"},{"name":"Summit Survivor","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1116350/84fd18e03a72fb3fd6b20a503a959185d5c81a06.jpg"},{"name":"Cave Crawler","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1116350/f5bda09f3677a7bab4508b058df38d4eb677b9c4.jpg"},{"name":"Gate Crasher","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1116350/5246e8f66aca9e22f84feaecfd70931747b3f441.jpg"},{"name":"Secure the Market","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1116350/db87a1927c899fecae3c411fe6f3c3a0dcdd72d3.jpg"},{"name":"Secure The Lower City","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1116350/565d4de208f1f321dc716394b9d61501aa231b56.jpg"},{"name":"Neighborhood Watch","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1116350/593be979ebe36211bac646c4572ac24a0cd826db.jpg"},{"name":"Midstack Mayhem","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1116350/fc8dd236dc1ddfb7fca40113e843bf635b83ec6e.jpg"},{"name":"Bomb Squad","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1116350/b84c918c8e95dc331972a3261901e38c329bdc02.jpg"},{"name":"Ascending the Hoist","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1116350/ea8d9e501b3aa86c1ea272ea9936c1ce6c48812d.jpg"}],"total":20},"background":"https://shared.akam